--------------------------------------------------
⚠️ PACKAGING INSTRUCTIONS FOR RETROHACKLAB
--------------------------------------------------
1. Drop your raw decrypted .deb tweaks into this directory.
2. Run 'dpkg-scanpackages' to parse binary headers into the master 'Packages' index.
3. Compress indexes using gzip and bzip2.
4. Update the root 'Release' manifest.

